I've been using this App for over a year - and it was great at first. When you edit it creates a folder on your phone named "pictures". Lately I've been editing and when I go to the file the pictures are gone. Frustrating, but that's not the worst! I've lost over a 100 photos - just disappeared from...Full ReviewI've been using this App for over a year - and it was great at first. When you edit it creates a folder on your phone named "pictures". Lately I've been editing and when I go to the file the pictures are gone. Frustrating, but that's not the worst! I've lost over a 100 photos - just disappeared from my folder. Now I've noticed that every time I edit photos they just  disappear along with a lot of other pictures I've edited in the past. I am extremely disappointed and disgusted. I've lost a lot of great memories. I've uninstalled the app and deleted it.
